{"tid":1637931,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【抗暴之戰】連登仔話罷食元氣難過香港獨立？ 日本藝人Soko推介兩間抵食壽司小店","createTime":"2019-10-08T06:47:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T13:02:24.000Z","uid":202798,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2f9e1bd78d79a5f6beee6be6dad5a597c2fc4dd5","tid":1637931,"uid":202798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T06:47:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20191008/60117213\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191008%2F60117213&d=nKAZF5zAPcG2WvBXR7hnIpnDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=ef2f7a04\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191008%2F60117213&h=825673f1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20191008/60117213</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0nkATpj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0nkATpj.jpg&h=450c713f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rwdiRbu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrwdiRbu.jpg&h=b2312685&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">好想吃呑拿魚</span></span></strong><br />\n早前美心集團創辦人長女伍淑清，於日內瓦出席「聯合國人權理事會會議」，公開撐送中條例，指示威者暴力，並為香港警察的過份武力洗白，網民於是發起抵制美心旗下各餐廳。但美心集團食肆於香港無處不在，包括：Starbucks、美心MX、美中鴨子等，更有日本料理店元氣、魚尚和千両。其實想吃價廉物美的日本菜有很多選擇，居港日本藝人和泉素行（Soko），現在就帶我們尋找壽司小店。<br />\n<br />\n於連登討論區，有網民指10.1國慶日大遊行後，元氣壽司外仍然大排長龍，當中不乏年輕人。連登仔女更激烈討論，戲言「罷吃元氣難過香港獨立」、「我正式宣佈香港人係冇骨氣」。記者於是來到香港城市大學和香港中文大學，調查大學生們對於抵制美心集團的看法。<br />\n<br />\n受訪大學生：不給伍淑清賺錢機會<br />\n受訪的60人全體支持抵制美心，有同學指「這些中資機構，賺香港人錢，卻違背香港人的訴求，應該抵制」，亦有同學指「即使美心跟伍淑清已割席，她仍持有股份，絕不會給錢她賺」。記者提供美心旗下餐廳的品牌嘜頭，請同學選出最難罷食的餐廳。票選結果出爐，最多同學選Starbucks和元氣壽司。針對元氣壽司而言，同學指平日很喜歡光顧元氣，因性價比高，指「元氣是中低價位壽司的選擇，最愛吃炸蝦卷和茶碗蒸。」亦有人指甚少光顧，因「政府曾化驗到壽司好多蟲，特別是三文魚，生吃有一定風險。」<br />\n<br />\nSoko第一間推介的，是位於坑口，開業約兩年的鮪世市場。小店只有8個座位，但食物全部即點即做，早前8.5三罷，員工亦有響應罷市。Soko推介$125的壽司套餐，一次過品嚐到赤身、中拖羅、大拖羅和吞拿魚碎；他指：「脂肪油香和赤身的濃味融在一起。」而食客亦可以單點壽司。Soko另外點了四款，共$45，包括三文魚、三文魚腩、炙燒三文魚和玉子燒；小店採用的三文魚是即日返貨馬上烹調給客人吃，故特別新鮮。「老闆跟供應商關係好，所以價錢能維持在合理的水平。水準高、價錢合理，更有人特意從柴灣和荃灣過來吃，物有所值。」<br />\n<br />\n第二間壽司小店，是位於太子的東京街；老闆早前接受電視台訪問，指生意跌了四成，但都絕對支持年輕人抗爭。小店有超過50款壽司選擇，老闆推介海膽和軟殼蟹手卷，Soko品嚐了炙燒三文魚手卷，「三文魚籽在口腔裏，一咬就爆出來；$45這個份量，滿足度好高！」"},{"pid":"2f55e8cf1cae24700cd61660fda9809b52f67a3c","tid":1637931,"uid":111088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T06:47:43.000Z","msg":"好似幾好"},{"pid":"eeab448a43ea6943928669f10ff79b1eb5bb12b7","tid":1637931,"uid":202798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f55e8cf1cae24700cd61660fda9809b52f67a3c","tid":1637931,"uid":111088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T06:47:43.000Z","msg":"好似幾好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T06:48:41.000Z","msg":"利申：食過，吞拿魚好食"},{"pid":"c6326b27cba1c2c18ea3e812bbb0b8591f44cc33","tid":1637931,"uid":45788,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T06:49:33.000Z","msg":"大大力懲罰佢！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢d公司一定食到佢冇貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fec5b8da05f31c32d3442d639372c69d202ba311","tid":1637931,"uid":202798,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c6326b27cba1c2c18ea3e812bbb0b8591f44cc33","tid":1637931,"uid":45788,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T06:49:33.000Z","msg":"大大力懲罰佢！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢d公司一定食到佢冇貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T06:51:46.000Z","msg":"鮪世午市唔算多，可以一戰"},{"pid":"dc2c8e31229ee5c3594466221f4eb2548f2721c1","tid":1637931,"uid":250951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T06:51:54.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5de9fc4ccaff1fe742766af170fba4a6fa8e106a","tid":1637931,"uid":45788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fec5b8da05f31c32d3442d639372c69d202ba311","tid":1637931,"uid":202798,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c6326b27cba1c2c18ea3e812bbb0b8591f44cc33","tid":1637931,"uid":45788,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T06:49:33.000Z","msg":"大大力懲罰佢！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢d公司一定食到佢冇貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T06:51:46.000Z","msg":"鮪世午市唔算多，可以一戰"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T06:53:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03cae7595145cad806000a03d0c0dabd5790007e","tid":1637931,"uid":202798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f9e1bd78d79a5f6beee6be6dad5a597c2fc4dd5","tid":1637931,"uid":202798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T06:47:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20191008/60117213\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191008%2F60117213&d=nKAZF5zAPcG2WvBXR7hnIpnDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=ef2f7a04\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191008%2F60117213&h=825673f1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/realtime/article/20191008/60117213</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0nkATpj.